lor":{"type":"Color","r":0.347059,"g":0.327451,"b":0.470588,"a":1},"text":"A Project I did following a tutorial in substance designer by Jimmy Malachier. I found some of the nodes are lacking a parallel, or if there is one it didn't have some of the functionality or fidelity. I did the best I could and I am new to the software so I'm sure I could have just gone about some things in a different way or simply don't understand how to use them to get similar results.\nTry plugging in other generators or tiled shapes into the height map inputs after the \"sculpting section.\"  I am in the discord so if you have any suggestions or questsions go ahead and send me a pm. @Bogey","size":{"x":540,"y":220}}],"connections":[{"from":"fbm2","from_port":0,"to":"bricks","to_port":1},{"from":"fbm2","from_port":0,"to":"bricks","to_port":2},{"from":"blend2","from_port":0,"to":"blend2_2","to_port":0},{"from":"blend2_2","from_port":0,"to":"blend2_3","to_port":0},{"from":"fill_to_gradient_3","from_port":0,"to":"blend2_3","to_port":1},{"from":"blend2_3","from_port":0,"to":"blend2_4","to_port":0},{"from":"fill_to_random_color","from_port":0,"to":"decompose","to_port":0},{"from":"decompose","from_port":2,"to":"blend2_4","to_port":1},{"from":"fill_to_gradient","from_port":0,"to":"blend2","to_port":1},{"from":"fill_to_gradient_2","from_port":0,"to":"blend2_2","to_port":1},{"from":"reroute_3","from_port":0,"to":"fill_to_gradient_2","to_port":0},{"from":"reroute_3","from_port":0,"to":"fill_to_gradient_3","to_port":0},{"from":"reroute_3","from_port":0,"to":"fill_to_gradient","to_port":0},{"from":"reroute_3","from_port":0,"to":"fill_to_random_color","to_port":0},{"from":"fbm2_2","from_port":0,"to":"warp","to_port":0},{"from":"fbm2_2","from_port":0,"to":"warp","to_port":1},{"from":"uniform","from_port":0,"to":"blend2_5","to_port":0},{"from":"uniform_2","from_port":0,"to":"blend2_5","to_port":1},{"from":"warp","from_port":0,"to":"tones_range","to_port":0},{"from":"tones_range","from_port":0,"to":"bl